Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.44,0:00:17.04,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}微风轻吻着脸庞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.61,0:00:20.60,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}用着一种怀念的温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.05,0:00:29.39,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}吹干流下的泪珠轻拂而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.82,0:00:39.72,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}不管是谁 对未来都有着一股不安的期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.97,0:00:48.74,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}就朝着明天大步迈进吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.18,0:00:51.25,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}GUNPARADE MARCH
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.25,0:00:57.71,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}总有一天会觉醒的 真实之心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.75,0:01:05.06,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}现在就伸出双手去感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.29,0:01:12.63,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}在这开始变化的世界 立刻前往探寻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.83,0:01:20.14,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}牵系着你的手绝不再分离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.81,0:01:22.80,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}因为有你在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.18,0:01:27.81,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}所以一定找寻的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.76,0:01:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(暑假时正门封闭 请由侧门进出)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.88,0:02:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「第三话  夏日感伤」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}熊本县的各位听众早安\N各位早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.59,0:02:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}今天看来也会相当的炎热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.99,0:02:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}请各位不要屈服于酷暑跟幻兽 好好打起精神来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.56,0:02:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}首先就是「每日今天」的专栏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.06,0:02:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}今天是8月13日 各位知道是什么日子吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.00,0:02:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.34,0:02:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.24,0:02:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}今天是国民义务兵役法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.47,0:02:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}通称学生征兵法通过的日子\N(国会通过学生征兵法)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.61,0:02:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么快就说出来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.38,0:02:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}21年前 也就是1978年的今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.75,0:02:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}国会通过了学生征兵法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.62,0:02:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}也就是说 至今保护我们的兵役制度是在今天诞生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.59,0:02:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}当时的媒体做出了下列的报导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.66,0:02:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}目前成为国会焦点的国民义务兵役法案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.07,0:02:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}已经在本日多数表决通过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.97,0:03:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}由芝村重工业所开发对幻兽最新人型战车AMTT-500
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.38,0:03:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}为避免适任驾驶员之成年人口损失过多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.05,0:03:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}并且将适任者保持在一定人数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.65,0:03:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}朝野党团至今都为此进行协调
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.63,0:03:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}经过这次的决议 明年起征兵年龄限制降为16岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.93,0:03:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}这是为了人类未来而做出的痛苦抉择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.57,0:03:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}对于今后的青少年而言…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.84,0:03:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要关掉啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.08,0:03:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就看这种节目 心情会不好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们平常不都是看这台的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不喜欢里头的内容啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.52,0:03:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫做学生征兵法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.95,0:03:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了那玩意 害我宝贵的青春都浪费掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.82,0:03:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟有谁会希望在这间破宿舍跟一群大男人一起住啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.60,0:03:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也可以在立法之前就放弃兵役 去做其他工作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.60,0:04:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20年前？你开玩笑的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.38,0:04:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想我的不幸 就是从21年前的今天开始的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.58,0:04:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本拥有世间罕见俊美的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.62,0:04:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在应该在大海或深山 跟众多美女一起享受青春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.29,0:04:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是用你的牢骚结尾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.13,0:04:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.73,0:04:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀、石头、布！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.94,0:04:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是速水啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.31,0:04:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的赌运也太差了吧～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.58,0:04:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正输在那种地方也没什么好难过的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.15,0:04:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水他平常虽然倒楣 不过在战场上倒是很幸运呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.39,0:04:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神毕竟是公平的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.66,0:04:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.66,0:05:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说好像不是这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.60,0:05:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中或许也有不太公平的神吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.17,0:05:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.92,0:05:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是真的吗\N-真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.49,0:05:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是因为她 所以现在才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.36,0:05:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种时候 应该在大海或深山享受青春的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.13,0:05:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是没办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.00,0:05:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟不知道什么时候要出动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.63,0:05:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们特别班是没有暑假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.21,0:05:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在不妨碍任务的状况下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.87,0:05:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自调整 休息个几天而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.32,0:06:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能问你一件事情吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.89,0:06:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.39,0:06:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不公平的神是指什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指真纪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.47,0:06:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真纪她是个不幸少女喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.48,0:06:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-田边你没事吧\N-我很喜欢这个的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.18,0:06:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马铃薯炖肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.69,0:06:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是我最喜欢吃的菜 就一定会不小心打翻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没摔坏 碗没摔坏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.00,0:06:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样就会摔坏 那田边可就赔不完咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.44,0:06:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.94,0:06:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真纪是世界上最不幸的女生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.18,0:07:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么啦 太没精神了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.05,0:07:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样还算是士兵吗 还算是5121部队的驾驶员吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.98,0:07:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 驾驶员需要的是反射神经跟判断力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.26,0:07:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟体力应该没有关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.43,0:07:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.63,0:07:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HWT操作失灵的话怎么办 最后还不是要靠体力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.70,0:07:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当作有幻兽在追你们 给我拼命跑吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.44,0:07:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个健身迷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.28,0:08:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 他刚刚不是跑在前面的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.15,0:08:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩一圈了 全力冲刺！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.16,0:08:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.80,0:08:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是芝村同学的请假单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.66,0:08:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是不是写错了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.10,0:08:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休假的连络地址跟家里的不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是有她自己的理由吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.95,0:08:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泷川 帮我拿一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己拿啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.36,0:08:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我再也动不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.86,0:08:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑操场50圈加单杠翻身500次 而且重复三次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.10,0:09:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还加上青蛙跳跟仰卧起坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.34,0:09:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们根本就不是人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.74,0:09:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是受不了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.97,0:09:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急广播、紧急广播
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.38,0:09:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5121部队所有男性请注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.98,0:09:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽速前往校舍屋顶集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.38,0:09:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一次 请尽速前往校舍屋顶集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.49,0:09:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事情了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.82,0:09:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.26,0:09:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊们要帮你们～保～养～眼～睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.73,0:09:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.50,0:09:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还能动嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.71,0:09:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么啦 这到底…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.11,0:09:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借过借过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.62,0:09:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都来了还在发什么呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.59,0:09:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快来这里坐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.36,0:10:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 我想起来了 今天是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.18,0:10:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TAMAYA～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.45,0:10:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天果然还是要这样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.63,0:10:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未央、未央！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未央～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.40,0:10:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.07,0:10:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的衣服一模一样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.84,0:10:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她一年前转学过来时一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.58,0:10:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.16,0:11:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壬生屋是来递补茜的缺额…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.09,0:11:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜过世至今也一年了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.37,0:11:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年将会是她第一次的中元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.39,0:11:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜过世至今也一年了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.62,0:11:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年将会是她第一次的中元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.84,0:11:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是CVα-6 距离目标上空还有60秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.91,0:12:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水、速水同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.15,0:12:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水同学！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.22,0:12:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.79,0:12:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表现出至今训练的成果就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.06,0:12:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.79,0:12:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泷川跟濑户口也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.06,0:12:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过于意识到这是实战 跟训练时采取一样的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.74,0:12:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有茜 千万不要大意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.00,0:12:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.31,0:12:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是身为驾驶员的我 没有特别去意识到这是实战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.94,0:12:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前锋是速水跟茜 后卫濑户口跟泷川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.09,0:12:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HWT发动倒数30秒 准备出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.69,0:12:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.20,0:12:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5 4 3 2 1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气冲过去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.13,0:13:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.74,0:13:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.14,0:13:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12点钟方向有大量敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正往这边接近过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.25,0:13:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前距离170 140 120 100
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.03,0:13:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,90 75 50 40…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.04,0:14:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.14,0:14:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.20,0:14:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5121部队…5121部队！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.30,0:14:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主脑确认形式为A-3 座标417·525
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.81,0:14:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PBE作战开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.58,0:14:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近部队请进入安全范围回避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.31,0:14:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5121部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.08,0:14:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5121部队请尽速撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.38,0:14:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5121部队！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.72,0:14:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.60,0:15:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PBE引爆前倒数15秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.04,0:15:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三号机赶快撤退！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.51,0:15:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中元吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.64,0:15:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14号上午的降雨机率为70%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.15,0:15:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预计熊本县将会有豪雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.65,0:16:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请各位外出时不要忘记带伞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.02,0:16:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本节目是由为人类开拓未来的芝村关系企业所提供
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.47,0:16:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么那么坐立不安啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.54,0:16:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水…速水呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.54,0:16:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说他要到街上一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.81,0:16:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 原来速水不在的话 你就寂寞到食不下咽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.74,0:16:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 我才不管速水 问题是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.55,0:16:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是小舞也不在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.48,0:16:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.42,0:16:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水那家伙 难道说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.15,0:16:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这猪头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.76,0:16:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会想到这种方向去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.69,0:16:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不纯洁！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.63,0:16:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个完全没有那种感觉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.93,0:16:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.56,0:16:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村说她要去车站一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.20,0:16:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车站？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.34,0:16:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的特快车来回票跟床位券
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.07,0:16:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您的惠顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放水灯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要帮去年过世的朋友过中元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.27,0:17:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家约好明天晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.51,0:17:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.81,0:17:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村同学的老家在哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.18,0:17:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要探亲对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.22,0:17:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你有向芳野老师请假…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.92,0:17:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟你没关系吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.99,0:17:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对、对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.96,0:18:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.73,0:18:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.10,0:18:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 有什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.47,0:18:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是汽油车 这是汽油车耶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.28,0:18:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟这个比起来 电动车根本比芋头还不如呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样啦 真不像话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.85,0:18:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 这种VIP专用车怎么会在我们学校啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.86,0:18:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.29,0:18:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问是芝村舞小姐的同学吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.23,0:18:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问舞小姐人在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.30,0:19:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村她应该是坐昨天的夜车回老家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.24,0:19:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我随时都有注意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.14,0:19:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.71,0:19:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.22,0:19:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小舞该不会是富翁的千金吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.49,0:19:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更新更新！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.99,0:19:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 芝村果然还是那个芝村集团吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.16,0:19:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.91,0:19:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年没见面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.69,0:19:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些就是全部了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.43,0:20:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.33,0:20:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护身符？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.43,0:20:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望小茜在天国不会害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.70,0:20:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜她…会害怕？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.97,0:20:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.11,0:20:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望望美我感觉得到 小茜她真的很害怕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.68,0:20:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以了 她一定不会害怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泷川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.67,0:20:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有三长两短的话 记得在水灯上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.21,0:20:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡妞笔记本对吧 我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.51,0:20:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要汽油车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.25,0:20:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会沉下去吧 而且你又不能坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.69,0:21:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.13,0:21:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望不会再有人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.67,0:21:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.12,0:21:47.47,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}最重要的心情 总是过于接近无法传达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.14,0:21:59.81,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}擦肩而过时的悲伤 在我的内心紧紧纠结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.41,0:22:06.32,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}雨过天睛 光珠般的雨滴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.45,0:22:11.98,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}我将其收集起来 藉以思念你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.46,0:22:19.30,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}没人知道我将前往何处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.67,0:22:26.07,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}只有明日的风描绘着我的轨迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.21,0:22:31.51,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}随着时代变动的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.01,0:22:37.58,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}即使迷失在困惑里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.72,0:22:43.92,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}也要抱紧这相遇的奇迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.36,0:22:53.93,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}走吧 一同前去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.04,0:22:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.50,0:23:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双人座就是有两个人坐一台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.94,0:23:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人坐一台会被警察骂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.04,0:23:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过骂到小舞的话 她会很可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.65,0:23:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以应该是另一个人会被骂吧
